songs.title: Tell Me Why
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
Try to turn on my TV to get you out of my head
Feeling something deep inside
That I just won't admit
It's not like I don't want to come in (want to come in)
I just don't know why I can't
Stop feeling like this

[Chorus]
Tell me why (why, why)
Does it hurt so bad
Tell me why (why, why)
Does it make me mad
Tell me why
Tell me why

[Verse 2]
Now you're off with someone else
And I'm stuck at home
It's getting late and now I'm feeling so alone
Now I can see the storm's not going to clear
(not going to clear)
Dressed in my pain and out of my tears

[Chorus]
Tell me why (why, why)
Does it hurt so bad (you make it hurt so bad)
Tell me why (why, why)
Does it make me mad
Tell me why
Tell me why

[Bridge]
Now I'm in pain because
Losing you is not all I lost this time

[Chorus]
Tell me why (why)
Does it hurt so bad
Tell me why (why)
Does it make me mad

(Why, why)
(Why, why)

[Chorus]
Tell me why (why, why)
Does it hurt so bad (why does it hurt so bad)
Tell me why (why, why)
Does it make me mad
